<br>

<div class="row justify-content-center text-white text-special">
    <h2 class="text-white m-2">Welcome To Pickem Dota 2</h2>
</div>

<div class="container mt-2 mb-2">
    <div class="row">
            <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" style="width: 100%; height: 20rem;">
                <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                </ol>
                <div class="carousel-inner" style="width: 100%;">
                    <div class="carousel-item p-2 active">
                        <div class="row justify-content-center text-white text-special">
                            <h2 class="text-white">Upcoming Tournament</h2>
                            <% nxt = Tournament.find_by('end_date > ?', Date.today) %>
                            <div class="col-8 text-center"><%= nxt.title %></div>
                            <div class="col-8 text-center"><%= image_tag(nxt.banner, style: "width:70%;height:70%") if nxt.banner.attached? %></div>
                            <div class="col-8 text-center">From <%= nxt.start_date %> To <%= nxt.end_date %></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item p-2">
                        <div class="row justify-content-center text-special">
                            <h2 class="text-white">Prize Allocation</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row justify-content-center text-special p-4">
                            <ul>
                                <li>First Prize: RM3600</li>
                                <li>Second Prize: RM1800</li>
                                <li>Third Prize: RM1000</li>
                                <li>Forth Prize: RM 850</li>
                                <li>Fifth Prize: RM 750</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item p-2">
                        <div class="row justify-content-center text-white text-special">
                            <h2 class="text-white">How To Participate?</h2>
                            <ol>
                                <li>
                                    <p>Account will be activated upon confirmation of payment. Please do not hesitate to contact admin for any inquiries.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>Anyone is eligble to register & participate to compete for the grand prize!</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>Admins will not be held responsible for any questions left unanswered. We advise all players to complete their answers & to double check 60minutes prior to match time to avoid any problems.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>Each game along with the rewards, will evolve over time, based on feedback recieved from players, in order to create best pick-em ever created! We hope to receive more feedback from the community.</p>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                </a>
                <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                </a>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

<br><br>